				h1.articleheading who is SILICON ARTIST?
				p.articletext Steven always looked for easy money where he could find it - email scams, pyramid schemes, door-to-door break-ins, etc. Everything would have been different if he hadn't robbed the wrong person. Kidnapped by hired goons and strapped to an operating table, Steven was injected with an experimental serum designed to turn human flesh in a pliable fluid. He life was ruined. Everything would have been different.

				p.articletext Troubled con artist and professional thief Silicon Artist is one of the newest members of Knox's Villain Underground criminal organization. With his ability to stretch and shape his skin like clay, Silicon Artist is a slippery opponent in any fight. In addition, Silicon Artist loves to pester his opponents with insults and imitations just for his own weird pleasure. He may not be the most bloodthirsty member of the Viilain Underground, but this invincible mess always seems to bounce back. 
