				h1.articleheading what is SILICON ARTIST's skill?
				p.articletext Silicon Artist possesses an awesome range of superpowers, even if he's constantly using them to irritate his Villain Underground compatriots. A victim of a dangerous scientific experiment, Silicon Artist is able to stretch his body into any shape with a thought. Not only can he use this to impersonate others, but also slip into small spaces and turn parts of his body into a makeshift weapons. Silicon Artist's STRETCH skill lets players do the same via creating ever-changing copies of the Utilities and Crossovers in their deck.

